&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are Kaizen Gaming&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kaizen Gaming, the team powering Betano, is one of the biggest GameTech companies in the world, operating in 20 markets. We always aim to leverage cutting-edge technology, providing the best experience to our millions of customers who trust us for their entertainment.&lt;/p&gt;
