&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Let&#39;s start with the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Back in 2021 we aimed to reform our team and increase its size twofold. After successfully achieving this goal,and looking ahead to 2025, our focus remains on crafting our skills and making Kaizen a &quot;Mobile First&quot; company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our mobile team consists of 35+ Engineers, 20 of them are Android Engineers and they are complemented by Software Engineers in Test, for the quality perspective.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Engineers work either in our Mobile Infrastructure team or they contribute directly to our cross-functional feature squads.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our mobile applications are used by millions of people across many countries and continents. We use Swift/Kotlin to create a quality codebase, we desire to improve our technical practices and move to the next technical level, and we will heavily invest in covering our codebase with tests on all levels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tech Stack: Kotlin, Dagger2, JUnit, Kotlin Flows and Coroutines, Jetpack Compose, in-house navigation library, ViewBinding, Detekt, Custom MVC,&amp;nbsp; MVP and MVVM, GitLab for source code management, Bitrise for CI/CD, Transifex for translations, Figma for designs, Firebase&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Supportive Stack/Processes: Scrum/Kanban, Jira / Confluence, Firebase / Google Analytics / Google Tag Manager, Pair programming, Unit testing, UI Tests&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Being part of the Infrastructure team, you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help shape the new era of the company mobile wise;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement our technology roadmap to the highest of quality standards;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Affect the technological vision of the Android chapter;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work on challenging tasks and constantly hone your technical skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Being part of the feature squads, you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Impact our clients worldwide;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with other crafts in cross functional teams;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work on state of art features with great business value;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Constantly evolve and upgrade your game.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid experience in Android technologies (Kotlin programming skills);&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated AI-first mindset, actively leveraging AI tools and assistants to improve productivity, problem-solving, and decision-making. Continuously exploring new AI capabilities and championing their practical adoption within teams, using AI as a natural part of day-to-day work rather than a supplementary tool;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion to level-up our apps.&lt;/li&gt;
