&lt;li&gt;Support administrative activities related to hospitality projects, including purchase requests, payment follow-up, invoice tracking and validation, and internal documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with inventory control of hospitality materials, gifts, and branded items, ensuring accurate records and availability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support internal stakeholders with hospitality-related requests and day-to-day operational needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in post-event activities, including feedback collection, reporting, and operational follow-up.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute ideas to improve administrative processes, operational organization, and the overall guest experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help ensure premium service standards are consistently delivered across all hospitality initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
