&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educational background (completed or in progress) in Hospitality, Tourism, Marketing, Communications, Business Administration, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Initial professional experience, internships, or academic projects related to Hospitality, Events, Tourism, Customer Service, Administrative Support, Marketing, or similar areas.&lt;/li&gt;
