&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Let’s start with the program&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We are calling on the next generation of talent to join the Kaizen Gaming Internship Program 2026.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Designed for students eager to learn by doing, grow in a global environment, and contribute to a high-performing team, this program offers the opportunity to gain hands-on experience while working on real business challenges from day one.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;At Kaizen Gaming, interns are encouraged to take ownership, collaborate across teams, and continuously develop their skills in a fast-paced environment driven by innovation, technology, and customer-centricity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;More than an internship, this is an opportunity to accelerate your growth, expand your perspective, and become part of a global team that is constantly evolving and shaping the future of digital entertainment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As a Kaizen Gaming Intern, you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to real business projects and initiatives within your assigned team;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with colleagues and stakeholders across different functions and markets;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support day-to-day operations while gaining exposure to strategic business challenges;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop critical thinking and problem-solving skills through hands-on experience;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring fresh ideas, curiosity, and new perspectives to the team;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn from experienced professionals through mentorship, feedback, and continuous development opportunities;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build meaningful connections in a collaborative and international environment;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Embody our values of People First, Passion, Customer Lens, Get Things Done, Continuous Improvement, and One Team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We are looking for students who demonstrate potential, curiosity, and a strong desire to learn.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Successful candidates will have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Currently pursuing a Bachelor&#39;s degree in any field of study;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enrolled from the 2nd year onwards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Availability to work part-time during morning and/or afternoon hours, Monday through Friday;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Availability to work in a hybrid model in São Paulo, Brazil;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and collaboration skills;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A proactive mindset and willingness to take initiative;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curiosity, adaptability, and eagerness to learn in a dynamic environment;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organizational skills and attention to detail;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work effectively in a team-oriented environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;

